text:
There are some workarounds - You could use css and dynamically create classes, ie:

```&lt;style&gt;

.contact-cool-name {
  display:none;
}
.contact-jack--show {
 display:block;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;div class="contact-cool-name contact-{{contact.firstname}}--show"&gt;
You have a cool name
&lt;/div&gt;```
